Package CAMs_App.service

Class ColouredTextPrinter

java.lang.Object
CAMs_App.service.ColouredTextPrinter
public class ColouredTextPrinter extends Object
The class ColouredTextPrinter prints color text in the console using ANSI escape codes. The class includes methods for printing text of various colors and a rainbow effect for each color
Since:
2023-10-25
